	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64358370"><p>I have been driving manual for most of my life, and yes I like it much better.  In the winter it get much better control in slippery conditions. But:</p><p>I think there is is no need for a transmission for EVs.  I remember reading about this long ago about how electric vehicles 100+ years ago claimed that as an advantage.  Do modern EVs have a transmission ?  I kind of doubt it.</p></div>
