<div id="comment_status_64358472" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_64358472" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_64358472" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64358472" name="comment_link_64358472" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23274788&amp;cid=64358472" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64358472)" >There have always been practical advantages</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64358472" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64358472); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
