	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64358580"><p>There have been very few automatic motorcycles.<br>Hondamatic (I think hydrostatic)<br>Rokon (snowmobile)<br>Husqvarna (4 speed automatic)<br>Some have CVT transmissions<br>Honda (Z50) was clutch less but you still shifted<br>There are auto clutches for dirt bikes (Rekluse, others)<br>And electric motorcycles are single speed</p><p>EV on motorcyles has a limit.  Weight greatly affects handling so you can't just add more batteries. You'll probably never see a hybrid.</p></div>
	</div>

